      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>tortillas</strong> to a plate and pop them in the <strong>microwave</strong> for 20 secs or until warmed through</p><p>While the tortillas are in the microwave, combine your <strong>chipotle paste</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) with your <strong>mayo</strong>, a drizzle of<strong> olive oil</strong> and 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp] </span><strong>cold water</strong> in a bowl<strong> </strong>– this is your <strong>chipotle mayo</strong></p>",
