    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the salmon is cooked, peel off and discard the skin</p><p>Break the <strong>cooked salmon</strong> apart into bite-sized pieces with a wooden spoon and remove from the heat – these are your <strong>blackened salmon chunks</strong></p>",
